						<summary>

						<p>This is damaged and fragmentary. It seems to record a gift of land for burning a lamp (in the temple) by a lady, who is stated to be the daughter of some religious teacher <hi rend="italic">(gurudēva)</hi> at Māṅgāḍu in Puliyūrk-kōṭṭam.</p>						

